  "title": "(✈️🏝️Travel Opportunities!!) Brand Ambassadors",
  "description": "<p>🌟 Brand Ambassador (Events & Roadshows) 🌟</p><p></p><p>Love talking to people? Enjoy events, pop-ups and high-energy environments? We’re looking for confident and friendly Brand Ambassadors to represent our clients at events and roadshows across Singapore.</p><p><br /></p><p>💼 What You’ll Be Doing</p><p><br /></p><p>Represent well-known brands at events, roadshows & activations</p><p>Engage the public through face-to-face interactions</p><p>Share product knowledge and create a positive brand experience</p><p>Drive brand awareness and support sales activities</p><p>Work closely with a fun, supportive team on-site</p><p><br /></p><p>👀 Who We’re Looking For</p><p><br /></p><p>Outgoing, confident, and comfortable talking to people</p><p>Positive attitude and willingness to learn</p><p>Good communication skills </p><p>No experience needed – training provided</p><p><br /></p><p>🎁 What You’ll Get</p><p><br /></p><p>Performance incentives</p><p>Hands-on experience in marketing, sales & brand activation</p><p>Personal development & communication skills training</p><p>Fun team culture with growth opportunities</p><p><br /></p><p>If you enjoy meeting new people and want real-world marketing experience, we want to hear from you 💥</p><p><br /></p><p>👉 Apply now and be part of our growing team!</p>",
